      "rationale": "The pedicle screw and rod are modeled as Ti-6Al-4V with isotropic linear elasticity below yield, transitioning to bilinear plasticity for post-yield response. Frictional contact (mu=0.2) at the set-screw interface is physically motivated and consistent with published literature. Model form uncertainty quantified via sensitivity analysis."
